        {
            "title": "水警聯海關西貢反走私 檢$806萬私煙扣查貨車快艇",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/72e33c825698ad032a908a088abc0d79/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250516/_2025051620183649148.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>警方懷疑近日有人在西貢一帶進行走私活動，經過深入調查及情報分析後，水警總區特遣隊、港外警區特遣隊、水警東分區聯同海關海域調查組人員今日（16日）凌晨在西貢一帶進行反走私行動。<br/>\n<br/>\n行動中，人員發現一艘沒有亮起航行燈的快艇駛至大網仔路沙下村對開沙灘，同時有數名可疑男子將貨物由快艇搬到岸上一輛貨車上。人員隨即採取行動，可疑男子立即跳上涉案快艇，高速往香港東面水域逃去。水警人員遂展開追截和搜索，最終在鄰近橋咀島斷頭洲西面的岸邊發現有關涉案快艇。<br/>\n<br/>\n人員在現場共檢獲179萬支懷疑私煙，估計市值約806萬元，應課稅值約592萬元，並扣查有關涉案貨車和快艇。案件交由海關人員繼續跟進調查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4252942/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"檢獲的私煙估計市值約806萬元，應課稅值約592萬元。警方提供\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/92dc8193399c959ffcf81652e5fd6194/2025-05/002_4__0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        檢獲的私煙估計市值約806萬元，應課稅值約592萬元。警方提供\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4252943/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"人員扣查有關涉案貨車。警方提供\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4622840d98beda52a10fc41e0c8db8f7/2025-05/001_7__0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        人員扣查有關涉案貨車。警方提供\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2069319/即時-港聞-水警聯海關西貢反走私-檢-806萬私煙扣查貨車快艇",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-16 20:36:19",
